            <p>with the community and help improve Open Data in Hong Kong! You can connect with the community online by participating on our <a href="https://plus.google.com/communities/107947866980791843501">Google+ page</a>, attend one of our <a href="/events">regular events</a>, or get involved with any of the <a href="/projects">ongoing projects</a>. Anyone can take part and lead, and it starts with first getting involved. Feel free to ask <a href="https://plus.google.com/communities/107947866980791843501">engage and ask a question</a> or drop us <a href="mailto:info@opendatahk.com">an email</a> to find out more.</p>
